{"4242290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "SPITE: Taking the Boss's Wife, Sister and Mother", "steam_appid": 4242290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4242290/extras/e055b99dc06b42af41f73f6ece979635.poster.avif?t=1776566531\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4242290/extras/e055b99dc06b42af41f73f6ece979635.webm?t=1776566531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4242290/extras/e055b99dc06b42af41f73f6ece979635.mp4?t=1776566531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>FEED. THE. BEAST.</u></i></strong><i><u> <strong>BREAK. THE. CAGE.</strong> <strong>TAKE. THEM. ALL.</strong></u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intro</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Back in school, your teacher once dubbed you a &quot;Maltese Tiger&quot;—a rare, mythical beast bursting with untamed potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But potential doesn’t pay the bills. The real world hit hard, and graduation left you dead broke and jobless. Desperate, you relied on your mother—a lifelong housekeeper for the wealthy Lee family—to secure you a bottom-rung job at the Lee Group’s real estate empire. The man running the show? Shane Lee. The golden-boy heir you grew up alongside. A man you once called a brother.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your mother fell critically ill, you went to Shane for help. Instead of a lifeline, he threw you a leash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With cold disdain, he ordered you to move into the estate and act as a glorified dog-sitter, banishing you to the same servant's quarters your mother used to occupy. His parting words before leaving on a month-long business trip? Wait there, and know your place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was only when you arrived at the sprawling Lee mansion that you discovered the sickening truth. Your mother’s &quot;room&quot; was nothing but a cage—a suffocating, five-foot-high utility closet where a grown man couldn't even stand up straight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But Shane forgot one crucial detail: lock a wild beast in a cage, and it doesn't become a tame dog. It just gets hungry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have exactly one month.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starting from this humiliating dungeon, you're going to claw your way up the manor's hierarchy—from the ground floor to the master suites. You will make your way into the bedrooms of the women Shane holds dearest: his sister, his wife, and his mother. You're going to use your cock to conquer his closest kin, dismantle his pride, and steal his entire life for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Heroines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4242290/extras/226a0240c91cbb61715ca946847e6291.poster.avif?t=1776566531\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4242290/extras/226a0240c91cbb61715ca946847e6291.webm?t=1776566531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4242290/extras/226a0240c91cbb61715ca946847e6291.mp4?t=1776566531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video clas